        (WebKit::ProxyRuntimeObject::classInfo):
        * Plugins/Hosted/ProxyRuntimeObject.mm: Added.
        (WebKit::ProxyRuntimeObject::ProxyRuntimeObject):
        (WebKit::ProxyRuntimeObject::~ProxyRuntimeObject):
        (WebKit::ProxyRuntimeObject::getInternalProxyInstance):

